to mislead anyone during
his confirmation hearings.

02:08.500 --> 02:13.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFF SESSIONS, U.S. Attorney
General: Let me state
this clearly, colleagues.

02:13.066 --> 02:18.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
I have never met with
or had any conversation
with any Russians or
any foreign officials

02:20.166 --> 02:25.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
