any such conversations by anyone
connected to the Trump campaign.

02:33.333 --> 02:38.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
I was your colleague in
this body for 20 years,
at least some of you.

02:40.366 --> 02:43.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And the suggestion that
I participated in any
collusion, that I was
aware of any collusion

02:48.200 --> 02:53.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
with the Russian government to
hurt this country, which I have
served with honor for 35 years,

02:55.866 --> 03:00.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
or to undermine the integrity
of our democratic process, is
an appalling and detestable lie.

03:03.433 --> 03:08.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The attorney
general also struck sparks today
when he declined several times

03:10.533 --> 03:14.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
