Mexico: Because you're
invoking executive privilege?

03:32.466 --> 03:33.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFF SESSIONS: I'm not able
to invoke executive privilege.

03:33.566 --> 03:34.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
That's the president's
prerogative.

03:34.466 --> 03:36.466 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

03:36.466 --> 03:40.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARTIN HEINRICH: Well, my
understanding is, you took an
oath, you raised your right hand

03:42.433 --> 03:45.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
