you would solemnly swear to tell
the truth, the whole truth and

03:46.433 --> 03:47.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
nothing but the truth.

03:47.800 --> 03:49.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And now you're not
answering questions.

03:49.600 --> 03:51.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
You're impeding
this investigation.

03:51.700 --> 03:55.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFF SESSIONS: I am protecting
the president' constitutional
right by not giving it away

03:59.066 --> 04:00.733 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
before he has a chance to...

04:00.733 --> 04:01.700 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
