04:01.700 --> 04:02.900 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

04:02.900 --> 04:04.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
MARTIN HEINRICH: You're
having it both ways.

04:04.966 --> 04:07.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JEFF SESSIONS: And,
secondly, I am telling
the truth in answering
your question, in saying

04:07.233 --> 04:11.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
