the Department of justice...

04:11.233 --> 04:13.266 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

04:13.266 --> 04:17.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFF SESSIONS: ... even and
to make sure the president has
full opportunity to decide these

04:18.433 --> 04:21.066 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
issues.

04:21.066 --> 04:24.433 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Now, in
