04:34.966 --> 04:37.066 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

04:37.066 --> 04:37.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SUSAN COLLINS (R), Maine: If
President Trump ordered you to
fire the special counsel, what

04:37.733 --> 04:39.800 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
