04:39.800 --> 04:41.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ROD ROSENSTEIN, Deputy Attorney
General Nominee: Senator, I'm
not going to follow any orders

04:41.266 --> 04:42.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
unless I believe those are
lawful and appropriate orders.

04:42.700 --> 04:44.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
If there were good cause,
I would consider it.

04:44.733 --> 04:45.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If there were not good
cause, it wouldn't matter
to me what anybody says.

04:45.266 --> 04:47.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

04:47.300 --> 04:47.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LINDSEY GRAHAM (R), South
Carolina: Do you know any reason
for a cause to fire Mr. Mueller

04:47.966 --> 04:49.200 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
