04:49.733 --> 04:51.833 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

04:51.833 --> 04:52.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LINDSEY GRAHAM: And that
would be your decision if
that ever happened, right?

04:52.766 --> 04:54.766 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ROD ROSENSTEIN: That's correct.

04:54.766 --> 04:56.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
