06:02.066 --> 06:06.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CARRIE JOHNSON, NPR: For Jeff
Sessions, the attorney general,
a qualified or limited success

06:06.833 --> 06:08.900 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
today.

06:08.900 --> 06:12.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
