on the FBI director, fired
FBI Director James Comey,

06:24.766 --> 06:29.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
and he also denied that
he had misled Congress
when he testified in his
confirmation hearings

06:31.033 --> 06:35.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
earlier this year that
he only had a couple
meetings with the Russians.

06:37.300 --> 06:41.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And he tried to clear up all
of those mistakes that he had
made, I think with some success

06:41.933 --> 06:43.933 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
today, Judy.

06:43.933 --> 06:47.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
