07:12.266 --> 07:16.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: I think
the answer that it was both
critical and it is just one more

07:16.633 --> 07:19.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
step along the road
of this investigation.

07:19.066 --> 07:23.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
