08:17.800 --> 08:20.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Again, you have been
following this very closely.

08:20.766 --> 08:24.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What questions do you still
have that the attorney general
either wasn't able to or

08:24.900 --> 08:27.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
