Democrats on the committee
today vowed to get answers
to those questions,

09:12.000 --> 09:13.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
come hell or high water.

09:13.500 --> 09:15.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Carrie, just a
quick question of clarification.

09:15.566 --> 09:20.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
