pardoning anyone in connection
with the Russia investigation.

09:20.033 --> 09:22.033 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
What are you referring to?

09:22.033 --> 09:26.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CARRIE JOHNSON: Well, he was
asked questions by Democrats
today, Jeff Sessions was, about

09:28.333 --> 09:31.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
