under investigators'
crosshairs right now.

09:52.800 --> 09:57.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We know that Flynn, in fact,
has tried to seek immunity,
so far without success.

09:57.466 --> 10:01.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Sessions was asked whether the
idea of pardoning anybody came
up, and he declined to answer

