10:06.400 --> 10:07.666 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I want to know more about that.

10:07.666 --> 10:09.700 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I think lawmakers do, too.

10:09.700 --> 10:13.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Carrie Johnson,
as we said, who covers the
