10:18.133 --> 10:22.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
And we turn now to our
panel of former Justice
Department officials.

10:22.400 --> 10:26.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
George Terwilliger served as
