10:29.166 --> 10:34.133 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Walter Dellinger served in
the Clinton administration
as assistant attorney
general and as acting

10:34.900 --> 10:36.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
