of national security.

10:44.733 --> 10:49.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Now, before I speak with them,
one issue today was former
FBI Director Comey's testimony

10:51.766 --> 10:55.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
about a February meeting in
the Oval Office, when everyone
else left, and the president

10:56.633 --> 10:58.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
