it say, and values of
a company that's become

42:40.066 --> 42:43.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
criticized for very
aggressive, unethical and
potentially illegal tactics.

42:44.266 --> 42:46.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Jeffrey Brown has the story.

42:46.300 --> 42:48.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Perhaps the
biggest immediate change, Uber's
chief executive and co-founder,

42:48.733 --> 42:52.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Travis Kalanick, will take an
indefinite leave of absence.

42:52.000 --> 42:56.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That comes after a personal
loss, the death of his mother,
but also coincides with a new

42:56.000 --> 43:00.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
report on company policy
and behavior led by former
Attorney General Eric Holder.

43:00.966 --> 43:05.933 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Uber's board of directors
reportedly adopted a
series of recommendations
from Holder, including

43:07.933 --> 43:11.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
more oversight of
leadership, new measures
to increase diversity
and inclusion, stricter

43:13.600 --> 43:16.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
guidelines for employee
behavior, and a pledge to change
Uber's core founding values.

43:18.800 --> 43:22.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Uber's problems grew after a
former engineer wrote a blog
post this past winter detailing

43:25.166 --> 43:27.866 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
how she had been sexually
harassed at the company
and how her managers
ignored her complaints.

43:28.800 --> 43:30.900 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
We're joined now
by Jessi Hempel.

43:30.900 --> 43:34.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
She head of editorial for
Backchannel, a tech and
business publishing site.

43:34.566 --> 43:36.566 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Welcome to you.

43:36.566 --> 43:39.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, is this, first of all,
a surprise that Travis
Kalanick is taking a leave?

43:39.600 --> 43:42.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And what further questions
does it raise for you?

43:42.433 --> 43:47.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JESSI HEMPEL, Backchannel: I
would say, in fact, it can't
be a surprise at this point

43:47.266 --> 43:48.633 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
that Travis is taking a leave.

43:48.633 --> 43:50.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Look, he's having a
hard personal time.

43:50.233 --> 43:52.166 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
He buried his mother on Friday.

43:52.166 --> 43:55.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But, beyond that,
the company needs it.

43:55.033 --> 43:56.700 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Shareholders are worried.

43:56.700 --> 43:59.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
