the company is going to
begin the lose value.

43:59.333 --> 44:04.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And as to what questions that
it raises for me, I think the
biggest question is, Travis

44:04.066 --> 44:09.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
