last few months has had.

47:23.100 --> 47:27.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And just very
briefly, Jessi, how much of all
this is being watched by other

47:27.500 --> 47:32.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
