charged with a similar kind
of culture in Silicon Valley?

47:32.400 --> 47:35.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JESSI HEMPEL: You make
a really great point.

47:35.233 --> 47:39.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
