for this, but this
isn't an Uber problem.

47:39.066 --> 47:43.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This is a problem that a lot of
start-ups have that have grown
to these massive valuations

47:43.533 --> 47:48.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
