on the charisma and the
vision of one founder.

47:48.266 --> 47:53.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think one thing that we
will see going forward is that
Silicon Valley will hopefully

47:55.333 --> 47:58.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
look itself in the mirror and
rethink some of the ways that
it structures these start-ups

47:58.233 --> 47:59.733 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to begin with.

47:59.733 --> 48:01.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Jessi Hempel
of Backchannel, thank you.

48:01.033 --> 48:02.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Thank you very much.

48:02.266 --> 48:06.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JESSI HEMPEL: Thank you.

48:06.833 --> 48:11.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
