48:37.733 --> 48:40.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
William Brangham takes a
look behind the numbers.

48:40.033 --> 48:45.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Today,
