a claim he's been making
for months: His policies

48:46.433 --> 48:48.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
are creating new jobs that
far surpass his predecessors.

48:48.533 --> 48:53.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP, President of the
United States: I think probably
seldom has any president

48:53.166 --> 48:57.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
