job-killing regulations.

49:02.366 --> 49:06.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we see it all over the
country, where jobs are starting
that would never have started,

49:06.666 --> 49:08.700 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
