49:08.700 --> 49:12.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Earlier this
month, the president claimed
he helped claim more than

49:12.133 --> 49:13.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
