correctly tweeted out a
lower number, 600,000.

49:27.400 --> 49:31.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
STEVEN RATTNER, Former Adviser
to President Obama: In my 40
years of being in and around

49:31.233 --> 49:36.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Washington and economic policy,
