tried to take credit
for on the job front.

49:39.866 --> 49:43.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Steve Rattner
is an analyst and Wall Street
financier who also headed

49:43.533 --> 49:46.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
President Obama's Auto
Industry Task Force.

49:46.533 --> 49:50.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
According to the Bureau of
Labor Statistics, in the four
months before President Trump's

49:50.466 --> 49:55.100 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
